HEADWORD: Ericinol
<hw>E*ric"i*nol</hw> <pr>(⟦esl⟧*r⟦icr⟧s"⟦icr⟧*n⟦omac⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. <ets>eric</ets>aceae the Heath family + L.
